2002-06-04  Naofumi Yasufuku  <naofumi@users.sourceforge.net>

	* gtk/gtkglwidget.c (gtk_widget_gl_realize) 
	(gtk_widget_gl_configure_event): gtk_quit_add (0, ...) will cause
	a problem with modal window. I use gtk_main_level () + 1 instead
	main_level 0. Thank you Igor ;-)

